## Customer Signup & Onboarding

### Signup Process (Self-Service)

**Goal:** Convert high-quality heat pump installers from lead generators to paying customers. Verify credentials upfront to maintain platform quality.

**User Journey:**

```
STAGE 1: Discovery & Interest
→ Installer finds TRADEEV2 via Google/word-of-mouth
→ Visits homepage, sees value prop: "Get qualified leads in your area"
→ Clicks "Become a Partner" or "Sign Up as Installer"

STAGE 2: Account Creation
→ /customer-signup page
→ Enters: email, password, confirm password
→ Email verified via confirmation link (TODO: Resend integration)
→ Redirected to /customer-signup

STAGE 3: Business Verification (Mandatory)
→ /customer-signup/verify
→ Enters business details:
  - Business name (required)
  - ABN / Company number (required - for lookup)
  - Phone (required)
  - Business email (auto-filled from signup email)
  - Service suburbs (checkboxes: Takapuna, Devonport, Birkenhead, etc.)
→ System verifies via EWRB / EPA Refrigerant License registry (TODO: API integration)
→ If verified → "✓ Credentials verified"
→ If not found → "We couldn't verify your credentials. Please upload proof."
  - Upload license/certificate (PDF, JPG)
  - Manual review by Alex (48-72 hour turnaround)

STAGE 4: Payment Method (Mandatory)
→ /customer-signup/payment
→ Stripe integration (TODO)
→ Collects:
  - Card details (visa, mastercard)
  - Billing name, address, postal code
→ Explanation: "You'll be charged $X per lead sent to you, billed monthly"
→ Test charge: $0.01 (to verify card works)

STAGE 5: Profile Setup (Mandatory)
→ /customer-signup/profile
→ Installer completes:
  - Business bio/description (100-300 chars)
  - Years in business
  - Specializations (residential, commercial, retrofit, etc.)
  - Photo (business/team photo) - optional for MVP, required later
  - Service radius (km from primary suburb)
→ Preview profile as end users will see it

STAGE 6: Review & Confirm
→ /customer-signup/review
→ Summary screen showing:
  - ✓ Email verified
  - ✓ Credentials verified / pending review
  - ✓ Payment method saved
  - ✓ Profile complete
  - Business name, service areas, bio
→ "Confirm & Start Receiving Leads" button
→ Terms checkbox: "I agree to TRADEEV2 terms of service"

STAGE 7: Welcome & First Login
→ Welcome email: "Your account is ready! Log in to see your first leads."
→ /customer-dashboard shows:
  - "Welcome, [Business Name]!"
  - "0 leads available for [Takapuna, Devonport]"
  - Quick start guide: "How to respond to leads"
  - Link to view metrics

STAGE 8: Ongoing
→ Installer logs in to /customer-dashboard
→ Sees: new leads, past leads, metrics, account settings
```

### Metrics Visible to Customers

Each installer sees their own performance dashboard:

- **Leads This Month:** Count of leads sent to them
- **Response Rate:** % of leads they've responded to
- **Interest Rate:** % of leads they marked "interested"
- **Profile Views:** How many customers viewed their profile (future)
- **Avg Response Time:** How quickly they respond (future)

### Customer Roles & Permissions

- **Status: Unverified** → Can sign up, enter details, but cannot receive leads until verified
- **Status: Verified (Manual)** → Credentials verified by Alex, can receive leads
- **Status: Verified (Auto)** → License verified via registry, can receive leads immediately
- **Status: Active** → Actively receiving leads
- **Status: Paused** → Installer paused, no new leads (account stays active)
- **Status: Inactive** → Unsubscribed, account closed

