## User Flows

### Flow 1: Customer Signs Up (Self-Service)
```
1. John (installer) visits tradeev2.nz/customer-signup
2. Enters email: john@coolcomfort.co.nz, password, confirm
3. Clicks "Create Account"
4. System sends email: "Verify your email address"
5. John clicks verification link in email
6. Redirected to /customer-signup/verify
7. Enters business details:
   - Business name: Cool Comfort Heat Pumps
   - ABN: 12 345 678 901
   - Phone: 021234567
   - Service suburbs: [Takapuna, Devonport, Birkenhead]
8. System looks up ABN in EWRB registry
9. If found: ✓ "Credentials verified" → proceeds
10. If not found: Shows "Upload proof of license" → Alex reviews (48-72h)
11. Redirected to /customer-signup/payment
12. Enters payment card details via Stripe
13. Test charge of $0.01 (verifies card works)
14. Redirected to /customer-signup/profile
15. Completes business profile:
    - Bio: "Expert heat pump installers with 15+ years experience..."
    - Years in business: 15
    - Specializations: [Residential, Retrofit]
    - Photo: uploads business photo (optional for MVP)
16. Redirected to /customer-signup/review
17. Reviews account summary
18. Clicks "Confirm & Start Receiving Leads"
19. Sees welcome message: "Your account is active!"
20. Redirected to /customer-dashboard
21. Can now view leads for [Takapuna, Devonport, Birkenhead]
```

### Flow 2: Customer Logs In
```
1. John goes to /installer-login
2. John enters email + password
3. System validates credentials against users table
4. System creates HTTP-only session cookie (or JWT)
5. John is redirected to /customer-dashboard
6. John can now:
   - View leads assigned to him
   - Mark leads as interested / not relevant
   - View profile
   - Change password
```

### Flow 3: Customer Views Metrics
```
1. John logs in to /customer-dashboard
2. Sees dashboard with metrics cards:
   - Leads This Month: 12
   - Response Rate: 75% (9 of 12 responded)
   - Interest Rate: 56% (5 of 9 interested)
3. Can click "View all leads" to see detailed list
4. Can click each metric to drill down into details
5. Sees trends over time (if available)
```

### Flow 4: Installer Forgets Password
```
1. John goes to /installer-login
2. John clicks "Forgot password?"
3. John enters his email
4. System checks if email exists, sends reset link:
   - Email: john@heatpumps.nz
   - Link: tradeev2.nz/password-reset-confirm/[uuid-token]
   - Token expires in 24 hours
5. John clicks link in email
6. John enters new password
7. System validates password, updates users table
8. John can now log in with new password
```

### Flow 5: Admin Logs In
```
1. Alex goes to /admin-login
2. Alex enters email + password
3. System validates credentials + checks role = 'admin'
4. System creates session
5. Alex is redirected to /admin
6. Alex can:
   - View all installers
   - Create new installer invites
   - View platform metrics
   - View all leads
```

